title: Mythoklash - 1978-1982 EP [2013]
description:
Mashup remixes of popular american songs from 1978 and 1982.

Tracks 01-11 = 1978 songs
Tracks 12-22 = 1982 songs
Source for track 6 chosen by Pat Myette
Source for track 12 chosen by Maxim Anderson
Track 23 remixed by the toilet

Arranged & mixed by Mythoklash

Artwork by Madame Gilles
www.madamegilles.tumblr.com

Thanks to: Madame Gilles, Dennis Woodroff, Maxim Anderson, Pat Myette, Gord Kirchin

Released by Neophile Records
